title: Ceiling Paper, 1905–15
inscribed: Printed in selvedge: "The Wallace Wallpaper Co. 307"
description:
Bead and reel quatrefoils connected by beadand real swags with floral medallions in each quatrefoil. In the resulting negative space are simplified flowers. Background of dash and dot pattern. Ground is light green. Printed in gold mica and greens. 
Printed in selvedge: "The Wallace Wallpaper Co. 307"

tombstone.epitaph:
Ceiling Paper, 1905–15.
1905–15. Machine-printed on paper, mica, liquid. Gift of Victorian Collectibles. 1979-91-1195.
